        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"I'll wait a little while, mammy,\" Elsie said, lying down again, \"but I must get up soon; for I wouldn't miss my walk with papa for a great deal.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
