        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "I'm so glad it has come.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "You ain't sick, nor sufferin' any way?\" exclaimed Chloe, in a tone of mingled concern and inquiry, as she hastily set down her broom, and came toward the bed, with a look of loving anxiety on her dark face.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Oh, yes, mammy! and that reminds me that papa said I must eat a cracker or something before I take my walk, because he thinks it isn't good for people to exercise much on an entirely empty stomach,\" said Elsie.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Will you get me one when you have done my curls?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "Had you a good night's rest?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Oh, yes, papa!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"In good season, too,\" he said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "Did you get something to eat?\" he asked, as he seated himself by the fire and drew her to his side.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Shall we not start soon?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "But alas! it cannot be, my darling,\" he added with a sigh.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000024_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000024_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "I cannot feel satisfied, and yet I believe few daughters love their fathers as well as she loves me;\" and fondly pressing the little hand he held, he looked down upon her with beaming eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "Breakfast-always a plentiful and inviting meal at Roselands-was already upon the table when they returned, and they brought to it appetites sufficiently keen to make it very enjoyable.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "Elsie spent the first hour after breakfast at the piano, practising, and the second in her papa's dressing room, studying and reciting to him; then they took a long ride on horseback, and when they returned she found that quite a number of the expected guests had already arrived.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "Among them was Caroline Howard, a favorite friend of Elsie's; a pretty, sweet tempered little girl, about a year older than herself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "Caroline had been away paying a long visit to some friends in the North, and so the two little girls had not met for nearly a year, and of course they had a great deal to say to each other.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "They chatted a few moments in the drawing room, and then Elsie carried her friend off with her to her own room, that they might go on with their talk while she was getting dressed for dinner.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"How pretty your hair is, Elsie,\" said Caroline, winding the glossy ringlets around her finger.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "I want to get a bracelet made for mamma, and she thinks so much of you, and your hair is such a lovely color, that I am sure she would be delighted with one made of it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"A Christmas gift is it to be?\" asked Elsie; \"but how will you get it done in time? for you know day after to morrow is Christmas.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Yes, I know; but if I could get into the city this afternoon, I think I might get them to promise it by to morrow night.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Of course I will; I don't want to spoil your beauty, though you are so much prettier than I,\" was Caroline's laughing rejoinder.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"There,\" she cried, holding up the severed ringlet, \"isn't it a beauty? but don't look scared, it will never be missed among so many; I don't even miss it myself, although I know it is gone.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Oh! you wouldn't be, Carry, if you knew him,\" Elsie answered, in her eager way; \"I was a little myself, at first, but now I love him so dearly, I never want to go anywhere without him.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "He was conversing with a strange gentleman, and his little girl stood quietly at his side, patiently waiting until he should be ready to give her his attention.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"I wish I could, my dear, but I have an engagement, which makes it quite impossible.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "You must wait until to morrow, when I can take you myself.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"But, papa, we want to go to day.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "Oh! please do say yes; we want to go so very much, and I'm sure we could do very nicely by ourselves.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"My little daughter forgets that when papa says no, she is never to ask again.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "Elsie blushed and hung her head.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000048_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000048_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "His manner was quite too grave and decided for her to venture another word.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"What is the matter?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "what does Elsie want?\" asked Adelaide, who was standing near, and had overheard enough to have some idea of the trouble.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
