        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Thank you,\" said her brother, looking very much pleased; \"that obviates the difficulty entirely.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
