        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "It was growing quite dark when the carriage again drove up the avenue; and mr Horace Dinsmore, who was beginning to feel a little anxious, came out to receive them, and ask what had detained them so long.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
