        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Long!\" said Adelaide, in a tone of surprise, \"you gentlemen really have no idea what an undertaking it is to shop.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
