        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"There is none here for you, sir,\" she replied, looking up into his face with an arch smile.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
