        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Indeed it does, and I feel richer in that possession than all the gold of California could make me,\" he said, pressing her to his heart.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
