        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "And she went on opening bundle after bundle, displaying their contents, and telling him for whom she intended them, until at last they had all been examined, and then she said, a little wearily, \"Now, mammy, please put them all away until to morrow.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000077_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3334/171008/3334_171008_000077_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "But first take off my things and get me ready to go downstairs.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3334_171008_000078_000000",
