        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"No, daughter,\" mr Dinsmore said in a gentle but firm tone; \"you are not ready to have them put away until the price of each has been set down in your book.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
