        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"Oh! papa,\" she cried in a startled tone, springing forward and taking hold of his hand, \"please, please don't look! you know you said I need not show you until after Christmas.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
