        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "Half an hour's work finished it all, and Elsie wiped her pen, and laid it away, saying joyously, \"Oh!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
