        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3334",
        "content": "\"No; I cannot often allow a departure from rules,\" he said kindly, but firmly; \"and to morrow night Elsie will find it harder to go to bed in season than to night.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
